			<dialogue>10000:此时曹操忙于治理蜀国，一面寻找逃亡的孔明。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:仲德，把这份书表撰写几份，发给原来的蜀国官员，能复职的就继续任用吧。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,21</storyAction>
			<dialogue>21,程昱:是。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,21</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:荀攸，百姓的情况如何？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,24</storyAction>
			<dialogue>24,荀攸:是。百姓几乎还怀念着蜀国，无心劳动终日哭泣的样子。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,24</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯，这也难怪……</dialogue>
			<storyAction>5,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:好，打开府库分发米粮给百姓，并免除蜀国百姓一年的赋税。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:让他们今后忘了蜀国，安心地做魏国的百姓吧。我们必须安抚民心，让他们归顺才行。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,24</storyAction>
			<dialogue>24,荀攸:是，属下即刻进行。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,24</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,23</storyAction>
			<dialogue>23,贾诩:治安似乎也已防患于未然了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,23</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯，不过还不能松懈管理，军中若有掠夺百姓财物的行为，无论官职大小一律斩首。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,23</storyAction>
			<dialogue>23,贾诩:是。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,23</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>5,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:好，内政方面就先这样吧。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:剩下的就是孔明了。司马懿，还没查到孔明的下落吗？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>19,司马懿:是的，不过已经派出众多耳目，不久就会有结果吧。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,19</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>4,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:哦，为什么花了这么久的时间！？</dialogue>
			<rolePlay>!骑兵,90,54,0,181</rolePlay>
			<dialogue>181,士兵:报。</dialogue>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>13,4,181</storyAction>
			<dialogue>181,士兵:主公，已经打听到孔明的下落了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>5,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:哦！有消息了吗？他现在何处？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>181,士兵:回禀主公，孔明收拾残兵据守在白帝城。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:白帝城！？原来如此。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,20</storyAction>
			<dialogue>20,荀彧:白帝城是刘备丧命之处，也是最险要的地方。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,20</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯，孔明小儿，难道打算和故主的亡魂迎击我们吗？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>5,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:好，吩咐军师们尽快完成刚才交付的任务，其他人马准备出发。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,0</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>19,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:必须早日除掉孔明。兵发白帝城！</dialogue>
